<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idc9c42964-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s364f"><num value="364f">§ 364f.</num><heading> Application to naming of offices or establishments</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Nothing in this chapter shall be construed as applying to the naming of the offices or establishments of any Federal agency.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idc9c42965-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598">(<ref href="/us/act/1947-07-25/ch330/s7">July 25, 1947, ch. 330, § 7</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/61/457">61 Stat. 457</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
